<section class="py-20 bg-cream" aria-labelledby="bio-heading">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-72 h-96 md:w-80 md:h-[28rem] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <img
              src="/images/dr-pradnya-about.jpg"
              alt="Dr. Pradnya Chittawadagi — Ayurvedic Physician and Research Scientist"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-gold-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg border border-gold-500/20">
            <span class="text-4xl">🌿</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wide uppercase text-forest-500 mb-3 block">
          Meet Your Physician
        </span>
        <h1 id="bio-heading" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-forest-900 mb-6">
          Dr. Pradnya Chittawadagi
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-earth-800/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Dr. Pradnya is a leading Ayurvedic physician, research scientist, and lifestyle medicine expert
          with over 12 years of clinical experience. She holds an MD in Ayurveda and a PhD in Clinical
          Ayurveda, making her one of the few practitioners who bridges rigorous academic research with
          hands-on patient care.
        </p>
        <p class="text-earth-800/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          A university topper and gold medalist, Dr. Pradnya trained extensively in Panchakarma —
          the classical Ayurvedic detoxification system — and has since treated thousands of patients
          dealing with chronic conditions like PCOS, diabetes, thyroid disorders, obesity, digestive
          issues, and stress-related ailments.
        </p>
        <p class="text-earth-800/80 leading-relaxed">
          Her approach is distinctive: she integrates time-tested Ayurvedic protocols with evidence-based
          modern science to design healing systems that actually work — for real people, in real lives.
          Every treatment plan is personalized to the patient's prakriti (constitution), lifestyle, and goals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
